"Brief Description: In the role of Relief Section Planner, you will be a vital contributor to our organisation's achievements by actively participating in planning activities within the Delivery Unit. Your core duty is to guarantee comprehensive coverage for our depots, especially during periods of Annual Leave and Sickness, and offering assistance to various sections for their planning and access requirements. You will collaborate closely with interdisciplinary teams, leveraging your proficiency in both access and systems planning. While your primary work location will be the Stockport Delivery Unit, travel across the entirety of Manchester's Delivery Unit and Depots will be necessary to meet resource demands."